Text: Beth Jenkins Resume and Cover LetterPST Could you please keep this in your email so I can have an electronic copy when I get to Houston Thanks B Forwarded by Beth JenkinsFPL EnergyFPL on PM Beth Jenkins AM To cc Subject Beth Jenkins Resume and Cover Letter I look forward to hearing from you Beth See attached file Enron Cover LetterdocSee attached file Beth Jenkins Resumedoc Enron Cover Letterdoc Beth Jenkins Resumedoc

Our plans for next weekPST We will be spending our first evening together at the luxurious Uncle Bills The website is currently under construction so it is unavailable I think you are familiar with the accommodations Friday we will get up and drive drive drive to the emerald waters of Destin FL Our trip is approximately miles or hrs minutes We are staying at a Holiday Inn on the beach Please see wwwholidayinndestincom for information on the accommodations Saturday we will lounge on the beach in the morning and then make our way to hot and humid New Orleans for an evening of revelry The trip is miles or hours minutes We will be staying at the International House It can be seen at wwwihhousecom Sunday we will be in no great rush to leave I need to find out more about what the music festival is all about We will be staying at the Lancaster in Houston located at wwwlancastercom The drive is hrs minutes and approximately miles Monday we rest but need to be around in case the movers come We will have logged miles on the Volvo and spent hours in the car together xo b
